Subject:[ug11] [IMP] Resume preparation
Body: Dear Students,

Hope you utilized the summer break fruitfully.

The students who will be sitting for placements or internship this year 
are advised to keep their one-page and two page resume ready by the end 
of this month.

For internship the resume submission will start by the second week of 
August. Resume verification will take place in first week of August. The 
internship openings will be shared with you a week in advance and you 
will have to apply for it by sending a mail with your resume in a 
specified format to intern.2014@gmail.com .

For Placement, master resume review will be done in August end (30th of 
August to 1st of September). Resume submission will start by mid of 
September. So you are advised to keep one page and two page resume ready 
and reviewed by some seniors. Also please make the necessary changes in 
your master resume related to Summer internship or projects.

For resume verification you will need to bring the original copy of your 
10th and 12th marksheets, transcripts , all the certificates and Project 
Verification forms.

For guidelines for making one and two page resume please visit 
http://spo.iitk.ac.in/preparation/resume.